 - Hibernate 4.2.21 with Hibernate Dialect Oracle10g (which is compatible up to 12 according to docs)
 - Oracle 12.2 (don&#39;t now exactly, I think 12.2, but maybe only 12.1)

The Hibernate version can&#39;t be upgraded as it is the last version that can be used with JPA 2.0, which is part of JavaEE 6 supported by Websphere Process Server 8.5.



